locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: Their predations continued, winning victory after victory, until the Republic finally begged the Jedi Council for aid.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: I would encourage you to consider the ramifications of such threats. You and I are linked, although I know not why or how.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: I will not go willingly, but I will not fight you if you attempt to force me out. Just know that, if I die, you might die too.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: One should not make such threats idly. Consider whether you are willing to suffer the consequences of this action, whatever they may be.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: A wise decision, although only necessary because of your foolishness in threatening our lives in the first instance.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: Very well. Let us hope, for both our sakes, that you are foolish enough to make such threats without the will to back them up.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: I would do anything to restore my connection to the Force.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: Get the hell off my ship. Now.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: Get out, or I'll throw you out the airlock.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: You're right - you can stay for now.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: I'll take that risk - you can walk out the airlock, or float out.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: On second thought, you can stay... for now.

locstring.label: Text
locstring.string: Let's... circle back to this another time.
